							<p class="i2_wwa_expl" style="">The Bitfury Group hosted its Third Annual Blockchain Summit in partnership with Bill Tai, with special support from Credit China Fintech, on Sir Richard Branson’s Necker Island from July 25-29, 2017. This unique Summit welcomed key global influencers in technology, civil society, non-profits and business to turn ideas into action about using Blockchain technology to make the world a better, more livable place – for all.

To learn more about the summit, visit <a href="http://www.neckerblockchainsummit.com/" target="blank">http://www.neckerblockchainsummit.com/</a>.</p>
